<plot>In Sacramento, Mexico, Antonio Ruiz is a bandit better known as 'El Halcon' (The Hawk). He had a twin brother who unfortunately died some time ago. At least this is what he thinks. In Seville, Spain, Juan Ruiz is a lawyer who once had a twin brother before he died. At least this is what he believes. So when Juan travels to Sacramento and finds Antonio alive the two brothers fall into each other's arms. They soon decide to join forces to fight against Enrique Ledesma, the governor of Sacramento, who murdered their father. But they also vie for the beautiful eyes of Luisa, who can't marry both of them.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?091710</url></doc>
